{"tid":518642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【與「海關拍賣網」劃清界線　台灣關務署：從未於臉書販售】512g手指","createTime":"2018-01-03T14:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T12:41:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fec850af508bc605779051016e2614315396d46a","tid":518642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"近日，Facebook 經常顯示一個叫「海關拍賣網」的廣告，聲稱「因年關將近，海關倉庫壓力過大」，決定將一批512G記憶體大平賣，不少香港及台灣網民都表示看過類似廣告。台灣關務署昨日就在 Facebook 回應，指「網路購物陷阱多，大家請小心」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣關務署專頁澄清，指 Facebook 上的「海關拍賣網」並非該署的官方網站，該署只會在官網公告拍賣資訊，絕對不會進行臉書或網站個人標售。<br />\n<br />\n財政部關務署今日（1月3日）再發正式聲明，指近日若干網頁或臉書以海關拍賣名義，低價出清大批隨身碟，關務署特別澄清，海關辦理沒收財物及逾期不報關等貨物之拍賣，僅於官方網站中公告相關標售作業，程序完全公開透明，從未自行或委託他人於網頁或臉書上販售拍賣物品。<br />\n<br />\n關務署重申，所屬各關均於官網上以公告方式，辦理海關沒收財物及逾期不報關等貨物之相關標售作業，並於開標前，將標售貨物各項資訊，包含所標售貨物、看貨日期、地點、押標日期、金額及開標時間、地點等事項公布於各關官網首頁或標售公告專區。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-03-2018/43362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-03-2018%2F43362&d=NSOsCbZezfDKkGynw5mBp49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=cbf27d38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-03-2018/43362</a><br />\n<br />\n#海關拍賣網 #關務署 #海關<br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=NSOsCbZezfDKkGynw5mBp49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=26041cf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=NSOsCbZezfDKkGynw5mBp49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5a3c8f0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\n<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/bpNcBn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbpNcBn&d=NSOsCbZezfDKkGynw5mBp49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2101dd98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/bpNcBn</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/IY4fHi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FIY4fHi&d=NSOsCbZezfDKkGynw5mBp49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=64ef4b80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/IY4fHi</a><br />\n--------------------<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\nTill our dreams come true, we'll fight on."},{"pid":"b6d02f3f2309857ddde7d5a8adda094228d92599","tid":518642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a07a8a260ea3c820cc5c135445f9ea367a88dd","tid":518642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbdc6443b43741fd3ad51fe099a8610bb87c30e","tid":518642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c10b515cde6685af3ccf19791e43e1979d2915","tid":518642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}